1
00:00:14,820 --> 00:00:17,140
[Sin and Love]

2
00:00:17,840 --> 00:00:20,720
[Episode 3]

3
00:00:35,120 --> 00:00:35,520
Hyung.

4
00:00:37,000 --> 00:00:37,930
Have some water.

5
00:00:40,080 --> 00:00:41,940
You left early yesterday, right?

6
00:00:42,620 --> 00:00:44,020
Did you see Kwon Hyukjae?

7
00:00:44,080 --> 00:00:44,680
Yes.

8
00:00:45,310 --> 00:00:46,710
He asked me about the bar.

9
00:00:46,750 --> 00:00:48,150
I said there wasn't much.

10
00:00:48,160 --> 00:00:49,090
That's about it.

11
00:00:49,700 --> 00:00:50,020
Why?

12
00:00:51,100 --> 00:00:52,230
Is something wrong?

13
00:00:53,120 --> 00:00:53,650
Nothing.

14
00:00:56,320 --> 00:00:57,850
I'm heading out for a while.

15
00:01:04,450 --> 00:01:05,420
Don't worry.

16
00:01:06,820 --> 00:01:07,950
I'll be watching...

17
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:09,880
your back.

18
00:01:35,630 --> 00:01:36,690
Yes, Officer Kwon.

19
00:01:37,880 --> 00:01:38,479
Sung Ho

20
00:01:39,950 --> 00:01:40,950
has made his move.

21
00:03:25,620 --> 00:03:26,280
Yoo Sehyun.

22
00:03:28,450 --> 00:03:29,510
What are you doing?

23
00:03:33,560 --> 00:03:34,290
You're here.

24
00:03:35,400 --> 00:03:35,920
Sit.

25
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:39,790
You used to hate things like that.

26
00:03:41,180 --> 00:03:41,980
Yes.

27
00:03:42,820 --> 00:03:43,680
In the past.

28
00:03:51,480 --> 00:03:53,280
The reason you called me here...

29
00:03:59,020 --> 00:03:59,550
Say it.

30
00:04:05,380 --> 00:04:06,820
You must be curious too—

31
00:04:08,850 --> 00:04:10,450
about why I left 5 years ago.

32
00:04:12,650 --> 00:04:13,380
Before that,

33
00:04:15,070 --> 00:04:16,320
try it.

34
00:04:16,320 --> 00:04:17,000
Hmm?

35
00:04:18,350 --> 00:04:20,610
Are you in this state
just to tell me that?

36
00:04:22,420 --> 00:04:23,520
This is who I am now.

37
00:04:23,920 --> 00:04:24,520
It's me.

38
00:04:30,620 --> 00:04:31,680
Are you kidding me?

39
00:04:39,840 --> 00:04:41,220
You're still the same.

40
00:04:47,250 --> 00:04:48,320
You didn't come

41
00:04:49,800 --> 00:04:51,120
to the airport 5 years ago—

42
00:04:51,120 --> 00:04:52,720
even up till the last moment.

43
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:56,180
I know.

44
00:06:06,230 --> 00:06:07,290
You must be curious

45
00:06:07,780 --> 00:06:09,420
why I left you 5 years ago.

46
00:06:10,730 --> 00:06:12,280
There's another reason.

47
00:06:15,480 --> 00:06:16,450
I know.

48
00:06:18,790 --> 00:06:19,520
Before you graduated,

49
00:06:19,520 --> 00:06:21,720
you were fooling around with other men.

50
00:06:22,580 --> 00:06:22,950
Look.

51
00:06:25,050 --> 00:06:26,950
I have videos and photos of it.

52
00:06:31,880 --> 00:06:33,080
It's not that simple.

53
00:06:35,350 --> 00:06:37,350
I can't tell you everything now.

54
00:06:39,350 --> 00:06:41,280
But the truth is far more dangerous

55
00:06:41,780 --> 00:06:42,840
than what you know.

56
00:06:53,880 --> 00:06:54,520
I'm sorry.

57
00:06:59,980 --> 00:07:01,380
I came looking for you...

58
00:07:02,020 --> 00:07:03,120
too late.

59
00:07:07,430 --> 00:07:08,280
No.

60
00:07:09,850 --> 00:07:11,580
What's there to be sorry about?

61
00:07:11,620 --> 00:07:12,850
It's my choice.

62
00:07:15,750 --> 00:07:17,280
I will help you by your side.

63
00:07:19,630 --> 00:07:20,830
I'll help you with...

64
00:07:23,280 --> 00:07:24,410
quitting drugs too.

65
00:07:28,680 --> 00:07:29,250
Sung Ho.

66
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,850
Before that,

67
00:07:40,780 --> 00:07:41,680
try this first.

68
00:07:42,880 --> 00:07:43,650
Here.

69
00:07:48,159 --> 00:07:49,960
You're not the Yoo Sehyun I know.

70
00:07:50,890 --> 00:07:51,820
Sehyun...

71
00:07:53,150 --> 00:07:54,650
would never be a druggie.

72
00:07:57,030 --> 00:07:57,860
No, this...

73
00:07:58,520 --> 00:07:59,320
This isn't...

74
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,720
just drugs.

75
00:08:03,900 --> 00:08:05,730
My dad died from doing drugs.

76
00:08:05,850 --> 00:08:06,950
Why would I do drugs?

77
00:08:06,950 --> 00:08:07,670
Trust me.

78
00:08:07,770 --> 00:08:08,550
Try it.

79
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,180
Wait.

80
00:08:22,950 --> 00:08:24,010
It's Kwon Hyukjae.

81
00:08:32,780 --> 00:08:33,950
Yes, Officer Kwon.

82
00:08:34,940 --> 00:08:35,740
Where are you?

83
00:08:36,370 --> 00:08:37,169
Are you alone?

84
00:08:37,330 --> 00:08:38,820
No, I-I'm alone.

85
00:08:40,780 --> 00:08:41,549
That's a lie.

86
00:08:42,210 --> 00:08:43,539
Sung Ho is there, right?

87
00:08:43,650 --> 00:08:45,780
I told you not to get involved with him.

88
00:08:45,950 --> 00:08:46,880
Record down your conversation with him

89
00:08:46,880 --> 00:08:48,680
word for word starting from right now.

90
00:08:48,680 --> 00:08:50,480
I'll be right there.

91
00:08:50,720 --> 00:08:51,980
Write it down and wait.

92
00:08:57,120 --> 00:08:57,620
Sung Ho.

93
00:08:58,400 --> 00:08:59,320
Leave quickly. It's dangerous here.

94
00:08:59,320 --> 00:08:59,980
Yoo Sehyun.

95
00:09:02,550 --> 00:09:04,210
Are you really an undercover?

96
00:09:06,850 --> 00:09:07,550
No.

97
00:09:09,950 --> 00:09:11,620
H-H-How could I do that?

98
00:09:11,930 --> 00:09:12,770
Please go.

99
00:09:12,890 --> 00:09:13,820
It's dangerous!

100
00:09:58,440 --> 00:09:59,320
I won't forget.

101
00:10:02,650 --> 00:10:04,310
I'll get to the bottom of this.

102
00:10:58,960 --> 00:10:59,580
Sehyun.

103
00:11:01,850 --> 00:11:02,550
I told you

104
00:11:02,550 --> 00:11:04,950
not to say anything unnecessary
to Sung Ho.

105
00:11:06,350 --> 00:11:07,780
Yet you even met him.

106
00:11:11,780 --> 00:11:12,250
What?

107
00:11:13,660 --> 00:11:14,780
Why not just tell him

108
00:11:14,780 --> 00:11:16,510
about you being an undercover?

109
00:11:19,200 --> 00:11:19,920
I didn't say

110
00:11:21,650 --> 00:11:22,850
anything about that.

111
00:11:24,150 --> 00:11:24,750
Happy now?

112
00:11:27,480 --> 00:11:28,050
Officer,

113
00:11:29,850 --> 00:11:30,650
I've been working for you

114
00:11:30,650 --> 00:11:31,950
for 5 years.

115
00:11:33,420 --> 00:11:34,280
But how long do I have to

116
00:11:34,280 --> 00:11:35,250
hold back?

117
00:11:35,650 --> 00:11:36,050
Huh?

118
00:11:37,520 --> 00:11:39,720
You must be mistaken.

119
00:11:41,020 --> 00:11:42,620
Your position, your future,

120
00:11:43,120 --> 00:11:44,020
and Sung Ho—

121
00:11:45,250 --> 00:11:46,580
they are all in my hands.

122
00:11:46,850 --> 00:11:48,310
If I move, you're all dead.

123
00:11:52,320 --> 00:11:52,820
What...

124
00:11:54,600 --> 00:11:55,730
do you want exactly?

125
00:12:02,610 --> 00:12:04,740
Sung Ho's father was a police officer.

126
00:12:06,650 --> 00:12:07,960
I need to get something from him.

127
00:12:07,960 --> 00:12:08,760
Bring it to me.

128
00:12:10,450 --> 00:12:12,420
Then I'll erase

129
00:12:13,380 --> 00:12:14,710
your past and identity.

130
00:12:16,150 --> 00:12:17,280
And I'll give you

131
00:12:17,320 --> 00:12:20,050
the identity of a police officer
you want so much.

132
00:12:20,580 --> 00:12:21,310
Bring Sung Ho

133
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,150
into this trap.

134
00:12:25,220 --> 00:12:25,950
Understand?

135
00:12:30,670 --> 00:12:32,000
Don't get him involved.

136
00:12:34,340 --> 00:12:35,240
I can't do

137
00:12:36,650 --> 00:12:37,580
anything to hurt

138
00:12:37,580 --> 00:12:38,420
him.

139
00:12:42,480 --> 00:12:43,920
You have no choice.

140
00:12:43,980 --> 00:12:45,910
How many times do I have to tell you?

141
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:49,380
Do as I say,

142
00:12:51,220 --> 00:12:53,050
or go to hell with him.

143
00:12:54,920 --> 00:12:55,720
It's up to you.

144
00:13:46,530 --> 00:13:47,860
You know Sung Ho, right?

145
00:13:49,750 --> 00:13:50,880
I heard he is the ace of the headquarters

146
00:13:50,880 --> 00:13:53,420
who just came back
from the special training in the US.

147
00:13:53,420 --> 00:13:55,020
I heard he's your first love.

148
00:14:01,420 --> 00:14:03,420
Say whatever you want, I don't care.

149
00:14:05,250 --> 00:14:06,580
But if you break the law,

150
00:14:08,420 --> 00:14:10,080
I will definitely arrest you.

151
00:14:34,080 --> 00:14:36,440
[Sin and Love]

